{"translation-revision-date":"2025-02-04T15:33:29+00:00","generator":"WP-CLI\/2.12.0","source":"admin-core\/assets\/build\/onboarding-app.js","domain":"messages","locale_data":{"messages":{"":{"domain":"messages","lang":"en","plural-forms":"nplurals=2; plural=(n != 1);"},"Spectra":["Espectros"],"Elementor":["Elementor"],"Bricks":["Tijolos"],"Other":["Outro"],"Email address":["Endere\u00e7o de e-mail"],"Reset":["Redefinir"],"Processing":["Processando"],"Access all of our pro templates when you upgrade your plan to CartFlows Pro today.":["Acesse todos os nossos modelos profissionais quando voc\u00ea atualizar seu plano para o CartFlows Pro hoje."],"Get CartFlows Pro":["Obtenha o CartFlows Pro"],"Back":["Voltar"],"Importing..":["Importando.."],"Active":["Ativo"],"Let's Start":["Vamos come\u00e7ar"],"Welcome to CartFlows":["Bem-vindo ao CartFlows"],"You're only minutes away from having a more profitable WooCommerce store! This short setup wizard will help you get started with CartFlows.":["Voc\u00ea est\u00e1 a apenas alguns minutos de ter uma loja WooCommerce mais lucrativa! Este assistente de configura\u00e7\u00e3o r\u00e1pida ajudar\u00e1 voc\u00ea a come\u00e7ar com o CartFlows."],"Save & Continue":["Salvar e Continuar"],"Saving":["Salvando"],"Hi there! Tell us which page builder you use.":["Ol\u00e1! Diga-nos qual construtor de p\u00e1ginas voc\u00ea usa."],"Install & Activate":["Instalar e Ativar"],"Installing Required Plugins":["Instalando Plugins Necess\u00e1rios"],"Since CartFlows uses WooCommerce, we'll set it up for you along with Cart Abandonment and Stripe Payments so you can recover abandoned orders and easily accept payments.":["Como o CartFlows usa o WooCommerce, vamos configur\u00e1-lo para voc\u00ea junto com o Abandono de Carrinho e Pagamentos via Stripe, para que voc\u00ea possa recuperar pedidos abandonados e aceitar pagamentos facilmente."],"Continuing\u2026":["Continuando\u2026"],"Continue":["Continuar"],"First Name":["Primeiro Nome"],"Please enter your name":["Por favor, insira seu nome"],"Enter Your Email":["Digite seu e-mail"],"Please Enter Name":["Por favor, insira o nome"],"Entered email address is not a valid email":["O endere\u00e7o de e-mail inserido n\u00e3o \u00e9 um e-mail v\u00e1lido"],"Please Enter Email ID":["Por favor, insira o ID de e-mail"],"Skip":["Pular"],"Select Color":["Selecionar Cor"],"Recommended":["Recomendado"],"Upload a Logo":["Carregar um logotipo"],"Change a Logo":["Alterar um logotipo"],"Remove logo":["Remover logotipo"],"Suggested Dimensions: 180x60 pixels":["Dimens\u00f5es sugeridas: 180x60 pixels"],"Oops!!! No templates found":["Ops!!! Nenhum modelo encontrado"],"Seems like no templates are available for chosen page editor. Don't worry, you can always import the store checkout template from the CartFlows setting menu.":["Parece que n\u00e3o h\u00e1 modelos dispon\u00edveis para o editor de p\u00e1gina escolhido. N\u00e3o se preocupe, voc\u00ea sempre pode importar o modelo de checkout da loja no menu de configura\u00e7\u00f5es do CartFlows."],"Skip to Next":["Pular para o pr\u00f3ximo"],"Now let's setup your new store checkout.":["Agora vamos configurar o checkout da sua nova loja."],"Choose one of the store checkout designs below. After setup you can change the text and color or even choose an entirely new store checkout design.":["Escolha um dos designs de checkout da loja abaixo. Ap\u00f3s a configura\u00e7\u00e3o, voc\u00ea pode alterar o texto e a cor ou at\u00e9 mesmo escolher um design de checkout de loja completamente novo."],"Import & Continue":["Importar e Continuar"],"Processing..":["Processando.."],"Importing Failed..":["Falha na importa\u00e7\u00e3o.."],"Change Primary Color":["Alterar Cor Prim\u00e1ria"],"Learn more about usage tracking":["Saiba mais sobre o rastreamento de uso"],"Documentation":[""],"Something went wrong":[""],"An unexpected error occurred while loading this section. Refreshing the page should fix the issue.":[""],"Go Back":[""],"Refresh Page":[""],"Block Builder":[""],"Beaver Builder":[""],"Exit Guided Setup":[""],"Awesome \ud83d\udc4d":[""],"Set up a high-converting checkout page in minutes":[""],"Recover abandoned orders with built-in cart abandonment":[""],"Accept payments easily with Stripe integration":[""],"Works seamlessly with your existing page builder":[""],"Boost revenue with upsells, downsells, and order bumps":[""],"CartFlows \u2014 Welcome Walkthrough":[""],"Get Started with Onboarding":[""],"CartFlows works with all page builders, so don't worry if your page builder is not in the list.":[""],"Great job! Now let's install some required plugins.":[""],"Not Installed":[""],"Previous templates":[""],"Next templates":[""],"One last step.":[""],"Let's setup email reports on how your store is doing.":[""],"Let CartFlows take the guesswork out of your checkout results. Each week your store will send you an email report with key metrics and insights. You also will receive emails from us to help your store sell more.":[""],"Help improve CartFlows by sharing non-sensitive usage data.":[""],"We don't collect any personal information\u2014just basic details like your PHP version, admin language, and which features you use.":[""],"Learn more":[""],"about what we collect and why.":[""],"High-converting checkout pages":[""],"Your store now has optimized checkout pages ready to convert visitors into customers.":[""],"Cart abandonment recovery":[""],"Automatically recover lost sales with built-in cart abandonment emails.":[""],"Revenue-boosting funnels":[""],"Upsells, downsells, and order bumps are ready to maximize your average order value.":[""],"Congratulations, You Did it! \ud83c\udf89":[""],"CartFlows is set up on your website! You're now ready to build high-converting sales funnels.":[""],"Here's What You've Unlocked:":[""],"Redirecting\u2026":[""],"Go To Dashboard":[""]}}}